name: Lease Agreement 1
description: A lease is a contractual arrangement calling for the user (referred to as the lesee) to pay the owner (the lessor) for use of an asset. The narrower term 'tenancy' describes a lease in which the tangible property is land (including at any vertical section such as airspace, storey of building or mine).
Use this template to arrange a house or apartment rental between you and your tenants with all core lease agreement units.
